Installation:

as the HDB dba (uchdba, lchdba, yakdba)
unpack at the HDB applications level (eg: /wrg/hdb/HDB_RELEASE.010427)
a directory usgsreports will be created
cd to usgsreports/src
type make

Run a test report for your site.
Note: This report will query for sites and pcodes defined in 
ref_hm_site_pcode. This probably is not everything.
I'm interested in hearing alternatives at
agilmore@uc.usbr.gov
